dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Pine County, Minnesota, C-13, Part A, Plate 3, Supplemental Bedrock Mapping
dc_description_s: Total magnetic intensity anomaly (relative to the earth's magnetic field), color coded.  Interpretation of magnetic data collected from airborne surveys, the map colors indicate the distribution and concentration of magnetic minerals (primarily iron-bearing) within the upper crust of the earth and associated detailed geologic interpretations of selected areas, scale 1:24,000; 1:300,000, Pine County.
